      "name": "Yield force and 40 mm displacement force QoI comparison",
      "description": "FEA yield force predictions fell within 7.1% of experimental values for all 11 constructs. Force at 40 mm displacement showed maximum deviation of 8.8%, within acceptance bounds. E/uval = 1.44 for this metric, below threshold."
    }
  ],
